{
  "uid": "nojv-exam-proctoring",
  "title": "NOJV — Exam Proctoring",
  "description": "Exam heartbeat health and SSE liveness for proctored sessions. SLO target: heartbeat miss rate < 1% (see docs/RELIABILITY.md).",
  "tags": ["nojv", "slo", "exam", "sse"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": true,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": { "from": "now-6h", "to": "now" },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "DS_PROMETHEUS",
        "type": "datasource",
        "label": "Datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "current": {
          "text": "grafanacloud-takalawang-prom",
          "value": "grafanacloud-takalawang-prom"
        },
        "hide": 0,
        "refresh": 1,
        "regex": "",
        "skipUrlSync": false
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Heartbeat misses per minute by gap bucket",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (gap_bucket) (rate(exam_heartbeat_miss_total[1m])) * 60",
          "legendFormat": "{{gap_bucket}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "bars", "lineWidth": 1, "fillOpacity": 60, "stacking": { "mode": "normal" } }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["last", "sum"] },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "SSE close events per minute (proxy for connection churn)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(sse_connection_duration_seconds_count[1m])) * 60",
          "legendFormat": "closes/min",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 0 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 15 }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single" }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "piechart",
      "title": "SSE close reasons (last 1h)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (close_reason) (rate(sse_connection_duration_seconds_count[1h]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{close_reason}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 8 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "short" },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "values": ["value", "percent"] },
        "pieType": "donut",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single" }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "SSE drops (server fault) per hour",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(sse_connection_dropped_total[1h])) * 3600",
          "legendFormat": "drops/hour",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 8 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10 }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single" }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Heartbeat miss rate (SLO target < 1%)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 16 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Heartbeat miss rate — SLO target `< 1%`\n\nWe currently emit `exam_heartbeat_miss_total` (counter) but do **not** emit a matching `exam_heartbeat_total` counter for successful heartbeats. To compute miss-rate-as-fraction we need both numerator and denominator.\n\n**Workaround until a denominator metric is added:**\n\n- The expected heartbeat cadence is one per active session per ~30s.\n- Cross-reference active session count from `apps/web` logs (`session.heartbeat`) and divide by `exam_heartbeat_miss_total` over the same window.\n\n**Action item:** instrument `exam_heartbeat_received_total` in `apps/web` so we can render this as a single PromQL expression. See `docs/RELIABILITY.md` SLO catalog."
      }
    }
  ]
}
